                "IOCH",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Focal Plane Detector Array of the",
                "S800 Spectrometer consists of a series of two x/y",
                "Position Sensitive Cathode Readout Drift Counters",
                "separated by 1 m, a segmented Ionization Chamber that",
                "is 41 cm deep and three scintillators that are 5, 10",
                "and 20 cm thick, respectively. All detectors have an",
                "active area of 30 cm x 59 cm."
              ]
